Overview

- D long stay (National) visa for applicants enrolled in an accredited higher education establishments (except citizens of countries listed

here (https://likumi.lv/ta/en/en/id/212364)

).
- After receiving a long stay visa (valid for up to 356 days ) and upon entering Latvia, students shall apply for a residence permit at the Office of Citizenship and Migration Affairs of Latvia (OCMA).
- Citizens of Algeria, South Sudan, Egypt, Yemen, Jordan, Cameroon, Kenya, Lebanon, Libya, Mali, Morocco, Nigeria, Somalia, Sudan, Tunisia, shall apply for residence permit at the Embassy first.
